      "description": "Well-kept car in good overall condition that presents nicely inside and out. It shows normal light wear for its age, with some minor cosmetic imperfections and signs of use, but nothing out of line for a solid, above-average driver. The interior is tidy, the exterior shows well, and overall this is an honest, enjoyable car a buyer can use and be proud of without expecting a flawless showpiece.",
