    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers an affordable path into ownership with solid value for the price. It shows cosmetic wear and age consistent with an older used car, but it remains a practical choice for a handy buyer, commuter backup, or project. Straightforward, honest, and priced to move, this is a chance to secure dependable transportation at a very accessible figure.",
