    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great chance to pick up a cheap runabout, learner car, or weekend project without spending a fortune. Honest car for the money, priced to sell, and ideal for someone handy or just needing basic transport on a budget. Come have a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with great bones and plenty of upside for the next owner. Starts, runs, and moves, with a drivetrain that feels willing and a chassis that still has usable life left in it. Shows cosmetic wear and needs finishing work, but that also means an honest platform you can sort, drive, or build without paying premium money up front. Good candidate for a budget commuter, weekend fixer, or parts-friendly restoration. Priced to move for someone who knows how to spot value in a mechanically straightforward package.",
      "price": 5900.0,
